Hennessy recently held its third “Code Henny” invite-only party. Top influential personalities came together in an exclusive Hennessy lovers circle at a secret villa in Nairobi, Lava Latte. The red-carpet event was led by Moet Hennessy’s Eastern Africa manager Alexandre Helaine and luxury PR consultant Lucia Musau. Guests were treated to live performances from Miss Karun, Steph Kapela and Ochunglo family. The Code Henny parties are about creating the Hennessy lover’s circle, to give them their own experience with Hennessy. Other notable personalities included Buddha Blaze, actress Sarah Teshna and celebrity make-up artist Phoina Tosha.